data.title: Lafayette Eye Associates
data.meta_description: Lafayette Eye Associates in Lafayette, Colorado and provides expert eye care exams, consults and services to patients in Boulder County.
data.text:
Mission Statement Lafayette Eye Associates, P.C. is dedicated to serving you with the best quality of care through our experience, technical skills and state-of-the-art equipment.

Our goal is to provide quality family eye care. We believe that the key to the success of our practice is in educating you about your eye health in a family-friendly environment.
